---
title: Cross-team production incident response
---
swimlane-beta LR
  accTitle: Production incident response across four teams
  accDescr: A customer report moves through support, platform operations, and engineering until service health is verified and the incident is closed.

  subgraph customer [Customer]
    report(["Report checkout failure"])
    confirm(["Confirm recovery"])
  end

  subgraph support [Customer Support]
    capture["Capture impact and evidence"]
    notice["Publish incident notice"]
    recovery["Publish recovery update"]
    close(["Close the incident"])
  end

  subgraph platform [Platform Operations]
    correlate["Correlate alerts and traces"]
    severity{"Major incident?"}
    mitigate["Apply safe mitigation"]
    observe["Watch service-level indicators"]
  end

  subgraph engineering [Engineering]
    reproduce["Reproduce the failure"]
    cause["Identify root cause"]
    fix["Implement and review fix"]
    deploy["Deploy progressively"]
  end

  report -->|"Ticket and diagnostics"| capture
  capture --> correlate --> severity
  severity -->|"Yes"| notice
  severity -->|"No"| reproduce
  notice --> mitigate
  mitigate --> reproduce --> cause --> fix --> deploy
  deploy --> observe
  observe -->|"Healthy"| recovery
  observe -->|"Regression"| mitigate
  recovery --> confirm --> close

  classDef terminal fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d,stroke-width:2px;
  classDef decision fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f,stroke-width:2px;
  classDef action fill:#eff6ff,stroke:#2563eb,color:#1e3a8a;
  class report,confirm,close terminal;
  class severity decision;
  class capture,notice,recovery,correlate,mitigate,observe,reproduce,cause,fix,deploy action;
